cargo run "Walk the dog"
cargo run "Fix rust code"
```

Each run will append a new task with auto-incremented ID. The JSON file will maintain a proper array structure, with the closing bracket moving appropriately as items are added. Initial run creates the file, subsequent runs append to it.

