PRODUCTION: Removing repo at "/repo/path"
Got element: Production element 42
TEST: Would add repo at "/repo/path"
TEST: Would move "/repo/path" to "/new/path"
TEST: Would remove repo at "/repo/path"
Got element: Test element 42
