   const socket = new WebSocket("ws://localhost:3000/ws/123");

   // From other origins will fail with 403
   ```

The solution:
- Centralizes origin checking in middleware
- Works alongside standard CORS configuration
- Properly handles WebSocket upgrade requests
- Rejects invalid origins with HTTP 403
- Maintains separation between HTTP and WebSocket security

